title.narrative: Private Sector Development: Business Link Pacific

description.narrative: Business Link Pacific supports the growth of Pacific small to medium enterprises through the development of sustainable in-country business advisory service networks. BLP aims to develop an effective market system where business advisory service providers offer quality services that respond to SME needs and SMEs use and pay for these services. BLP is currently implemented in Fiji, PNG, Samoa and Vanuatu.
